; nl-neutral-trace-live.fk — THE single command for a legible NL->neutral->NL
; query trace with rag concept match, choice paths, sizes, and north-star map:
;
;     ./fkwu --src cognition/tests/nl-neutral-trace-live.fk
;
; Default lanes: de "Wasser" and id "air", plus the neutral-pivot exemplar.
; Your own query: stage "<asserted-locale> <target-locale> <query text>" at
; .coherence-network/nl-neutral-trace-query.txt and re-run the same command.
;
